#<--- 72 characters --------------------------------------------------->
#
# Conventional Commits — semantic messages for humans and machines
# https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/
# Types (Angular convention):
# build, chore, ci, docs, feat, fix, perf, refactor, revert, style, test
#
#<--- pattern --------------------------------------------------------->
#
# <type>[(scope)][!]: <description>
#
# ! after type/scope marks a breaking change
#
# [optional body]
# - bullet points explaining what and why (not how)
#
# [optional footer(s)]
# BREAKING CHANGE: ...
# Refs: #123   Closes: #123
# Co-Authored-By: Name <email>
#
#<--- usage ----------------------------------------------------------->
# Enable locally:  git config commit.template .gitmessage
#
#<--- 72 characters --------------------------------------------------->
